{
  "texts": [
    "Following this, we evaluated the capability of each model to generate valid codes from a zero-shot prompt by comparing the produced codes with 2023 ICD-10-CM published codes.",
    "Furthermore, the production of \"exact match\" codes-defined as complete congruence between the provider-assigned code and the LLM-generated code-was assessed using both zero-shot and RAG-enhanced prompts for each model.",
    "The comparison between LLM-generated and provider-assigned codes was quantified through head-tohead percentages of reviewers' assigned accuracy and specificity \"wins\" to either LLM or provider codes.",
    "Both two LLMs (Llama-3.1, Qwen-2) and four physicians (two ED attendings and two ED residents) served as judges.",
    "We performed a qualitative analysis of GPT-4 generated codes using Llama-3.1's judgment."
  ]
}